    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>People who design, make, form, set up, or bring into existence an art work or other thing or activity, particularly where the creation is imaginative or inventive. For makers who execute the designs of other people, use the more general "makers" or the specific "executors (makers)."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
